libsweep
------------------------------------------
Low-level Scanse Sweep LiDAR library. Comes as C99 library sweep.h with
optional C++11 header sweep.hpp on top of it.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  libsweep-devel-1.3.0-1bl2
  libsweep1-1.3.0-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libprotobuf-devel-21.12-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/scanse/sweep-sdk

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/scanse/sweep-sdk/archive/refs/tags/v1.3.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libsweep-1.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libsweep-1.3.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libsweep-1.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsweep-1.3.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsweep1-1.3.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsweep-devel-1.3.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libsweep)
  /usr/bin/sweep-ctl.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libsweep.README
  /usr/share/doc/libsweep/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libsweep/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/libsweep/serial_protocol_spec.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/sweep-ctl.1.gz

(libsweep1)
  /usr/bin/cygsweep-1.dll

(libsweep-devel)
  /usr/include/sweep/config.h
  /usr/include/sweep/sweep.h
  /usr/include/sweep/sweep.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/sweep/SweepConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/libsweep.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libsweep.pc

